      "date": "2011-09-13 18:33:21.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: (5 inline comments)\n\nWe would like stats files to output valid YAML in the future, in order to make it easier to parse from monitoring tools.\n\nSee http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Yaml and http://www.yaml.org/spec/1.2/spec.html for details.\n\nThe above references also say that YAML indentation should be with spaces and not tabs. Please fix this in your patches as well.",
